.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, thai, spanish, malaysian, american, australian, colombian
7 different pets are kept: snake, lizard, ferret, hedgehog, cat, mouse, guinea-pig
 1. the american is on the left of the indonesian##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 3. the owner of the cat is the colombian##1
 4. the spanish is on the left of the australian##1
 5. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the malaysian is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the indonesian is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the malaysian##2
 9. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
10. the thai is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | colombian | american | indonesian | thai   | malaysian | spanish | australian |
| Pet           | cat | mouse     | lizard     | ferret | hedgehog   | snake   | guinea-pig    |

