.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, 7up, mirinda, milk
There are 7 different nationalities: spanish, canadian, thai, indonesian, brazilian, indian, japanese
 1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the thai##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the brazilian##1
 3. the indian is on the right of the indonesian##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the brazilian##1
 5. the spanish is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the indonesian is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the indian##2
 7. the person drinking coffee is in the middle##1
 8. the indonesian is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is the canadian##1
10. the spanish is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate    | 7up  | almond-milk  | coffee  | milk      | mirinda       | soy-milk |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian | indian | japanese | spanish | thai | canadian  |

