.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: pop, indie, gospel, trance, blues, hip-hop, funk
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, boat, taxi, snowmobile, roller, trike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the roller is the fan of indie##1
3. the person driving the airplane is between the fan of funk and the fan of pop##2
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the airplane is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the fan of pop##1
7. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
8. the person driving the boat is the fan of trance##1
9. the fan of blues is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | trance      | blues | pop | gospel | funk      | indie      | hip-hop |
| Transport     | boat | trike | quad-bike       | airplane | taxi | roller | snowmobile |

