.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  entrepreneur, lawyer, journalist, freelancer, photographer, fisherman, dancer
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: soccer, cricket, ice-hockey, sailing, surfing, swimming, skateboarding
1. the journalist is on the left of the dancer##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the photographer##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the lawyer is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the fisherman is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is surfing and the entrepreneur##2
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
8. the fisherman is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | photographer | entrepreneur | freelancer | fisherman | lawyer | journalist     | dancer |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | sailing    | skateboarding    | surfing      | cricket  | soccer | swimming |

