.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, sprite, juice, water, tea, soy-milk
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: tennis, snowboarding, golf, handball, badminton, water-polo, basketball
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person drinking water##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is basketball##2
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 7. the person who's sport is handball is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 9. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person drinking water##2
10. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | mirinda    | juice | sprite   | tea | soy-milk    | water |
| Sport      | handball | tennis | basketball    | snowboarding | badminton    | golf | water-polo  |

