.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, iced-tea, coffee, soy-milk, milk, almond-milk
The people have 7 different jobs:  lawyer, writer, electrician, scientist, bartender, videographer, mechanic
 1. the bartender is on the left of the scientist##1
 2. the lawyer is on the left of the electrician##1
 3. the videographer is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the bartender is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 7. the writer is on the right of the videographer##1
 8. the lawyer is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking 7up##2
11. the bartender is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | soy-milk   | 7up         | tea     | almond-milk              | milk    | coffee     |
| Job        | videographer | writer | bartender | scientist | mechanic | lawyer | electrician |

