.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: family, animation, zombie, sports, musical, mystery, spy
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, train, van, car, scooter, ship, bike
1. the person watching family movies is the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the scooter##2
4. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person driving the airplane is in the middle##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
9. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | sports     | mystery | musical | zombie | spy  | family |
| Transport     | van | car | scooter   | airplane     | bike    | train | ship   |

