.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, juice, hot-chocolate, sprite, lemonade, iced-tea
The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, skydiving, video-games, reading, traveling, chess, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is chess is the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking water##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is chess##2
9. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | water       | iced-tea         | sprite         | hot-chocolate   | juice        | lemonade |
| Hobby      | card-games | video-games | writing | traveling | skydiving | chess | reading  |

