4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is camping##2
8. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | camping | skydiving       | baking    | board-games | gardening | card-games     | writing       |
| Sport   | parkour    | surfing | soccer | swimming        | rugby | handball | biathlon |

