 3. the person watching action movies is between the person watching fantasy movies and the fan of gospel##2
 4. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
 5. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 6. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 7. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is the fan of indie##1
 9. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
10. the fan of soul is the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
