 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person eating cranberry is the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is the person eating broccoli##1
 8. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking mirinda and the person eating cranberry##2
